data.description: This is a well-kept and newly remodeled home, open floor plan, new paint, newer carpet, beautiful grey laminate, new cabinets and updated stone counter-tops. It has newer windows, A/C, one year old roofing, and a new storage shed. The yard has been well kept, sprinklers in front and back yard, both back and front yard are fully fenced as well. Backyard is private with wood fencing, tall mature trees and nice area to relax in front of the fire.
